Text: Hologram Doubles Your Protection Palm Solutions brought to you by InSync Online Hologram Doubles Your Protection Dear Jess Your Palmtm handheld quite smartly lets you to share your data when where and with whomever you wish So doesnt it drive you crazy when a perfect stranger insists on staring over your shoulder to read your private information Rest assured With ttools new SOLOvisiontm holographic Security Screen onlookers will get no further than the hologram SOLOvision adds two measures of protection one for your data the other for your handheld screen The thin film is imprinted with a clever holographic pattern that prevents prying eyes from discerning your data while you work It fits neatly on your handheld screen and features the Holoxtm lock and chain pattern SOLOvision also acts as a protective layer to prevent any nicks and scratches from damaging your screen SOLOvision comes in handy packs of four Find out more udjkfmrZecRRb The InSync Online Team The content of this message is based on your personal InSync Online profile To modify your profile or unsubscribe from InSync Online return to your InSync Online profile by clicking on the link below Or unsubscribe by replying to this message with unsubscribe as the subject line of the message C Palm Inc All rights reserved udkfmrZecRRQ Palmcom udEfmrZecRRV Palm Store udkfmrZecRRK InSync Online insyncdynisZVae MyPalm udqEfmrZecRRE
